\begin_layout Chapter
Actors identifying
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Visitor: all this people can only see the login form or registration form;
 they can also see a short description and the rules of the service.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
User : all this people, after successful login, are the only allow to see
 all available car, reserve a car and open it.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Operator: after the login, all these people can see all cars position and
 their condition (power and maintenance).
 They can also open and turn on cars.
 
